{
  "stem": "10272.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were marching-- we didn't know exactly where we were marching to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We already on the seventh day of the march.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were so exhausted, that if this-- if we wouldn't much into this town, into a town-- and our guards told us we are here, keep it up, another few-- another mile or two, we are-- we are dead.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this give us more energy to keep up this march, and to straighten out, and to show for the village, for the people of the city that we are not-- we are-- we are man.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We can walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we had this yellow band on our hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all-- they all stopped to-- to-- to watch us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who are these guys coming in?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had this on our-- we had the feet bags and we had everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had the blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were dressed up properly against the cold, with shoes, and boots, with-- with gloves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were-- we kept going now already, and we reached a place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, to halt, to stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We looked around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw there a building of three floor-- about three, four floor building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there's a sign that says, the Headquarters of the Nilosh-- Nilosh party or something or-- I don't know what it was, something about the Nilosh headquarters, in Kormend.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the city, we understood, it was called Kormend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's supposed to be a city which here, they will-- they will take us from here to Germany, or hand us over to the Germans, something like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we are waiting in line there, three, three, three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the first three guys were supposed to get inside, get registered, and pass a medical check up.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
